{
  "stem": "1975.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 311.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As you know, where-- they had four sectors, the American, the French, the British-- and, and, and the Russian was in [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the name of the street was the Ernst Schneller Strasse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were right there on the corner where we had our compound.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there were-- housed in the prisoners, the 16 main SS prisoners and their head, this captain.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we investigated them in a-- and prepared them for a process.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But going back to, to the Reich Chancellery, there were many Americans, I mean, American troops who used to come in there and some American visitors who came.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they used to take little souvenirs from the-- from the walls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I looked at them as crazy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, what are they taking, little pieces of tiles or, or walls?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I found that there were-- that was souvenir.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Plus the fact that Hitler's bunker underneath of this building was-- the doors were, like, a three-feet width that-- only the, the width of the door, not, not the-- I mean the--",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to keep them electrically, open and close them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now the electricity was out on account of the-- of, of the-- of the bombings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to move one of these doors, you need, like, four, four or five people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the bunker was like-- it has, like, Beton, which was concrete, maybe 5, 6-- 4 or 5, 6 meters of concrete.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You should have seen that, inside the bunker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have a, a, a camera to, to shoot pictures, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I wish I would have had, you know, with a flash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a whole-- a, a little city within, within, within the-- within the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
